UID:13191-1773478800-1773489600@durhamcentralpark.org
SUMMARY:Durham Farmers' Market
DESCRIPTION:The Durham Farmers’ Market is a community of farmers\, growers and crafters. We are strongly committed to local products: every item you see at the market was produced by the people selling it\, and it all comes from no more than 70 miles away. \nThe Durham Farmers’ Market open Saturdays mornings for local produce\, flowers\, crafts and more! The Wednesday Market is open from 3-6pm Wednesdays\, Mid-April through Mid-October \nIf you’d like more information about this week’s vendor list\, SNAP benefits and map\, visit durhamfarmersmarket.com \n\nWe are happy to offer Double Bucks to our SNAP clients. This means is a SNAP client has $10\, they receive $20 in tokens to spend at the winter market.\n\nEstamos muy contentos de ofrecer Double Bucks a nuestros clientes de SNAP. Esto significa que si un cliente de SNAP gasta $ 10\, recibirá $ 20 en tokens para gastar en productos frescos.\n\n\nAdditionally\, we offer a cash match program for other qualifying folks. To receive this benefit\, simply bring cash to the info table. Then\, we’ll double the amount with tokens. For example\, $10 in cash equals $20 in tokens.\n\nTambién ofrecemos un programa de contrapartida en efectivo para nuestros beneficiarios de SNAP que no tienen beneficios durante el mes\, clientes de WIC y miembros de la comunidad que viven en viviendas públicas. Para recibir este beneficio\, simplemente traiga efectivo a la tabla de información y duplicaremos la cantidad con tokens. Por ejemplo\, $ 10 en efectivo equivalen a $ 20 en fichas.
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/durham-farmers-market-8/2026-03-14/
LOCATION:Durham Central Park\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Farmers' Market,Featured Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://durhamcentralpark.org/content/uploads/HuthPhoto-KAH_6070.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Durham Farmers' Market":MAILTO:info@durhamfarmersmarket.com
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260314T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260314T180000
DTSTAMP:20260309T170554
CREATED:20260309T194959Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T195128Z
UID:13276-1773496800-1773511200@durhamcentralpark.org
SUMMARY:Mind\, Body & Soul Wellness Expo 2026
DESCRIPTION:Mind\, Body & Soul Wellness Expo 2026\nA Community Celebration of Health\, Hope\, and Healing\nJoin us for the Mind\, Body & Soul Wellness Expo 2026\, a free\, family-friendly community event dedicated to promoting mental health awareness\, holistic wellness\, and access to valuable resources for individuals and families across Durham and surrounding communities.\n\nHosted by NAMI Durham in partnership with Alliance Health and AmeriHealth Caritas North Carolina\, this exciting event brings together local mental health professionals\, healthcare providers\, wellness organizations\, faith leaders\, community advocates\, and service agencies all in one place.\n\nAttendees will have the opportunity to explore interactive wellness zones focused on the Mind\, Body\, and Soul\, offering education\, support\, and practical tools for improving overall well-being.\n\nWhat You Can Expect\n• Mental health education and community resources\n• Wellness and healthcare vendors\n• Mobile wellness screenings\n• Live music and entertainment\n• Line dancing and movement activities\n• A fun and engaging Kids Zone with games and family activities\n• Opportunities to connect with local organizations and support services\n• Raffles and giveaways throughout the event\nWhether you are looking for resources\, support\, inspiration\, or simply a day of wellness and community connection\, the Mind\, Body & Soul Wellness Expo offers something for everyone.\nEvent Details\n Location: Durham Central Park\n Date: Saturday\, March 14\, 2026\n Time: 2:00 PM – 6:00 PM\n Admission: Free and open to the public\n\nCome celebrate wellness\, strengthen community connections\, and take meaningful steps toward a healthier mind\, body\, and soul.\n\nMore information: Visit NAMIDurham.org
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/mind-body-soul-wellness-expo-2026/
LOCATION:Durham Central Park\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://durhamcentralpark.org/content/uploads/NAMI-Durham-expo.png
ORGANIZER;CN="NAMI Durham":MAILTO:contact@namidurhamnc.org
END:VEVENT
