UID:13267-1773583200-1773601200@durhamcentralpark.org
SUMMARY:The Sacred Source Holistic Marketplace
DESCRIPTION:The Sacred Source Holistic Marketplace is a heart-centered gathering created to nourish mind\, body\, and spirit while uplifting the local community. This unique marketplace brings together a beautiful collective of local holistic\, spiritual\, and healing vendors offering handcrafted goods\, natural wellness products\, energy services\, intuitive readings\, herbal remedies\, art\, and soul-aligned creations. It’s a space to discover tools for your personal healing journey\, support small businesses\, and connect with like-minded souls in a peaceful\, welcoming environment. \nGuests are also invited to experience a free community sound bath\, a deeply relaxing and restorative offering designed to help release stress\, reset your nervous system\, and bring you into a state of calm and balance. Whether you come to shop\, receive healing\, learn something new\, or simply soak in the high vibrational atmosphere\, Sacred Source is a place to slow down\, reconnect\, and feel supported. \nCome as you are\, bring a friend\, and allow yourself to be held in a space of warmth\, intention\, and collective healing. 
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/the-sacred-source-holistic-marketplace/
LOCATION:Durham Central Park\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://durhamcentralpark.org/content/uploads/March-15-2026-event-poster.png
ORGANIZER;CN="venuswraps":MAILTO:venuswraps@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
